PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant an Easement (ES-878) to the REGIONAL MUNICIPALITY OF OTTAWA-CARLETON, for a term of ninety-nine (99) years, over and across a strip of land situated in the Honey Gables neighbourhood between the Rideau River and River Road in Gloucester, for the installation of a sanitary sewer and a water main.
